--- Lynxiz / Axis / Lokk ---

Lynxiz smiles as she watches Trinity start to wake. "You need a 
CR little one, She picks up the injured bot, and heads over the 
small mound she was hiding behind. She opens a commlink to 
Grounded, "I need into the base, Trinity's injured. Is it safe to put 
down the shields?"

Axis looks out from behind his pod hiding place, and sees a bot, 
that looks like a Decepticon and the bot is firing on Windlord... he 
aims so as to not hit Windlord, and fires two charging laser blasts, 
and then arcs a missile at Shockwave. His laser starts to 
replenish, though his energy is being depleted and he knows that 
he will not be able to do much more. His missiles pack also reads 
a depleting ammunition supply. He shrugs to himself, and 
continues to charge his laser.

Lokk watches the fighting, not wanting to make any sudden 
gestures that would give away his position.
